Package org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.action

Class Summary
MenuActionLoadXGMML<T,C> MenuActionLoadXGMML launches an ActionEvent from the menu "File/Import/Dynamic Network/XGMML File..." to import dynamic networks into Cytoscape, and is also responsible to create the panel CytoPanel to control the visualization of dynamic graphical information.
MenuActionSelectVisibleEdges<T,C> MenuActionSelectVisibleEdges launches an ActionEvent from the menu "Select/Show all visible edges..." to select visible edges during dynamic visualizations.
MenuActionSelectVisibleNodes<T,C> MenuActionSelectVisibleNodes launches an ActionEvent from the menu "Select/Show all visible nodes..." to select visible nodes during dynamic visualizations.
